Vendored subset
---------------
Only the minimal set of Fortran modules needed for feature detection is
vendored. The Python wrapper, f2py signature files, netCDF helpers,
plotting utilities, spectral (SPHEREPACK) analysis and unused modules
(tend, diag_tend, ellipse, interpol, stat, sphere, thermodyn) are not
included.

  kind.f90                 type kind parameters
  const.f90                physical constants (needs -fno-range-check)
  config.f90               module-level thresholds
  derivatives.f90          finite-difference spatial derivatives
  diag.f90                 diagnostics (requires LAPACK: dsytrd/dsteqr/dorgtr)
  detect_rwb_contour.f90   Rossby wave breaking, contour method
  detect_lines.f90         line-tracking primitives
  utils.f90                smoothing and helpers
  detect.f90               all feature-detection subroutines

Local changes
-------------
None. Files are verbatim copies of the upstream snapshot. The ISO_C_BINDING
shim and all C/C++ wrapper code live under ../../dynlib/ and are not part
of upstream.

